Northwest Logistics Park is one of Dublin’s premier and most established logistics locations. The park is within 200m of the of the N2/N3 link road which provides dual carriageway access to the N2 (J3) & N3 (J2) routes, both of which are within 2kms of Northwest Logistics Park. Northwest Logistics Park is within 5kms of J5 & J6 on the M50 which provides motorway access to all of the main arterial routes from Dublin, to Dublin International Airport and the Port Tunnel. The logical location for Logistics.
